{"tid":803982,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[精神科藥] 有冇巴絲同我一樣","createTime":"2018-09-02T16:23:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T16:40:49.000Z","uid":50076,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"257004f0807f3485dcdddbd8348183aa75d5254a","tid":803982,"uid":50076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T16:23:17.000Z","msg":"小弟KEEP住食處方抗抑鬱藥，藥齡兩年半。<br />\n<br />\n近呢一年啲專注力同記憶差左好多，有好多野都專心唔到，就算係interview都好似發緊夢咁。<br />\n<br />\n同醫生講過好多次~ 佢次次都解釋完一兩句就叫我keep住個份量先。再係咁我真係會慢慢喪失工作能力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以前中學我係記憶好好，好少會唔記得野，但而家我有時連我昨日/今日食左咩/做左咩都唔記得，對日期既敏感度都低左好多，都唔知邊日打邊日咁......<br />\n<br />\n有時啲問題問完人，好快又問多次，仲話我煩之前問過，好驚自己有腦退化症... 岩岩先FG<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲同我一樣?"},{"pid":"19b922b7dc7cdbedaa2f72ee2856a173edf20c61","tid":803982,"uid":50076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T16:27:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51bc65f29bf1f75e0b6598b70d0d7467562a3a6a","tid":803982,"uid":50076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T16:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cfd58f17d8632bd1254443eb8590cb376a2a297","tid":803982,"uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T14:43:31.000Z","msg":"你問返專業人士啦"},{"pid":"b58c9146fc4407262e6810288465bd05678e445f","tid":803982,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T14:44:10.000Z","msg":"問醫生"},{"pid":"c25178c4331fb870b90f75479368d64aea8b4744","tid":803982,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T16:40:49.000Z","msg":"答你同你分享又會俾你鬧唔係專業人士出咩聲<br />\n唔答又話人小家<br />\n咩都你講晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}